Interface ConfigurationLoader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComponentLoader<TComponent>, Module
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonConfigurationLoader

    public ConfigurationLoader
extends ComponentLoader<TComponent>

    An extended interface ComponentLoader that is responsible for loading class Configuration instances.

    The method in which the configuration is loaded is to be defined through an implementation.
